A cyberpunk-style digital landscape showing a massive holographic form interface floating in a neon-lit cityscape at night. The form appears as an intricate three-dimensional web of glowing data nodes and flowing connection lines in electric blue and hot pink, morphing and transforming dynamically like liquid architecture. Below, rain-slicked streets reflect the brilliant light show above. Tiny silhouettes of people gather on platforms, gazing up at the magnificent data structure as streams of information pulse through interconnected pathways like digital blood vessels. The scene conveys raw technological power and transformation, with steam rising from vents and towering dark skyscrapers framing the ethereal floating construct.
